schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: Beautiful Twin Peaks home with level entry and plenty of parking. This home has had many upgrades and is move in ready for full time or weekend living. The main level offers 2 guest bedrooms and a full bathroom. Downstairs offers 2 master suites each with a full bathroom. The main living area offers vaulted wood beamed ceiling and an open concept floor plan. A wood burning fireplace and wood accented walls in the living room make this home feel warm and wonderful. Newer Roof. Double french doors lead out to the deck with views of mountain pine trees! Sellers have an assumable VA loan at 3%, call for details.
